---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
		<main>
			<h1>Neo Diego</h1>
			<img src="/neo-diego.jpg" alt="">
			<p>
				In a dystopian future, in the year 2100, the world has been rebuilt and reformed after the third world war, which culminated in a nuclear disaster that devastated much of the planet. The old countries had been disintegrated and the new states-cities of Tokyo, Hong Kong, New York, and Neo Diego rule the world. The latter, formerly known as San Diego, is the most powerful of all. Neo Diego is controlled by the mafia, the mega-corporations, and the corrupt government. The poor population is exploited by these three figures who compete for power. Their only hope lies with a private detective, a group of genepunks, and a mysterious vigilante biker. Together they will have to unravel a mystery that is unleashed after the disappearance of an engineer from the most important mega-corporation. If it is not done in time, the consequences for the city could be catastrophic.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
